                "text": "To estimate your monthly costs, enter the number of devices that utilize our registration workflows in a month.  The registration of a device is a one-time charge.  If the registration workflow is utilized for non-registration tasks, i.e. adding a set of new device attributes or rotating device certificates, these tasks will incur the same registration cost.",
